- `SC-Architecture.mmd`
  - End-to-end on-chain flow: deposit -> vault split -> hub/modules -> execution -> positions -> arena points -> withdraw.
  - Shows contract module relationships and infra dependencies.

- `Competitive-Positioning.mmd`
